IMAPAccount burningswell
Host imap.gmail.com
User roman.scherer@burningswell.com
PassCmd "pass Gmail/Burningswell"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore burningswell-remote
Account burningswell

MaildirStore burningswell-local
Path ~/Mail/burningswell/
Inbox ~/Mail/burningswell/inbox
Trash ~/Mail/burningswell/trash
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel burningswell
Far :burningswell-remote:
Near :burningswell-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Expunge None
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
Create Both
SyncState *


